---
import "./DevBlogPlaceholderStyles.scss";
---

<div id="dev-blog-page">

  <div id="dev-blog-header">
    <div id="dev-blog-header-content">
      <p class="dev-blog-eyebrow">Development Record</p>
      <h1>The Development Chronicle</h1>
      <p class="dev-blog-intro">
        The Development Chronicle is the firm's technical record: a structured
        account of architectural decisions, implementation constraints, and the
        periodic recalibrations that have characterised the current software
        programme. Authorship is attributed by role. Individual contributors are
        not identified by name, as per the firm's standard attribution protocol
        — a policy introduced following an incident in 2019 that the firm has
        since classified as formative.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="dev-blog-body">
    <div id="dev-blog-body-content">
      <div class="dev-blog-notice">
        <p class="notice-label">Archive Status</p>
        <p class="notice-text">
          No entries have been cleared for publication at this time. The archive
          is currently being prepared for external access. This preparation is
          ongoing.
        </p>
        <p class="notice-footer">The Correspondence Unit has been advised.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
